TI  - DeFaX: A Cross-Attention Fusion Framework for Robust and Explainable Deepfake Detection
AU  - Al-Imran, Md
AU  - Sheikh, Md Sifatullah
AU  - Kirtonia, Urmi
AU  - Arthi, Nuzath Tabassum
AU  - Ripon, Shamim
