TI  - Anti-Spoofing Liveliness Detector for Face Recognition System using You Only Looks Once version 8(YOLOv8)
AU  - Jain, Neha
AU  - Bhardwaj, Priyanka
AU  - Verma, Seema
AU  - Priyani, Juhi
AU  - Dahiya, Kushal
AB  - This method fights against bad guys fooling face recognition. Bad guys try sending pretend pictures or videos. They want to trick the system. Face recognition tech is used for mobiles, cameras, and IoT gadgets. If fooled, it is a big problem. This system uses deep learning to stop bad guys. It uses YOLOv8 to spot objects in pictures and videos fast and good. It combines YOLOv8 with deep learning. So it can tell if a face seen is real or fake. It works in live situations. This makes face recognition secure and can be trusted.The application goes through these steps: Capturing Live Video: Frames are recorded using a webcam. A pre-existing model spots faces in these frames. The model also checks how blurry each detected face is. Organizing Face Data: The discovered faces are sorted by whether they're real or fake. Their locations in the frames are noted. This structured data helps train and test machine learning models. Training YOLOv8 Model: The collected face data trains the YOLOv8 face detection model. This offline training finetunes settings to differentiate real and fake faces better. Real Time Face Detection: The trained model processes live video. It spots and labels faces as real or fake based on learned features. Users see these annotated frames with face authenticity feedback. Separately, a blur assessment uses the Laplacian math method. It measures the variance in pixel brightness within each face region. High variance equals clearer facial details. Low variance signals blurriness or lack of sharpness.The system blends advanced object spotting like YOLOv8, deep learning methods, and blur checking tools. It offers a full fix for finding and stopping spoofing attacks in face recognition systems. Tests show it works well and could make face recognition safer and more reliable in real life.
